      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Postrges/MySQL have plugins for:\n    1. geospatial index for lat/long\n    2. inverted index for the full text search",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "WRNlSe0dgQ7H7UyF4is8B",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 23788.721228193972,
      "y": 1440.096718996177,
      "width": 734.739013671875,
      "height": 300,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "#9775fa",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "dashed",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b6d",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1851359661,
      "version": 410,
      "versionNonce": 1144155779,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1780046459328,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "How would you efficiently calculate and update the average rating for businesses\n    ❌ calculate the average rating on the fly\n           - AVG(r.rating) AS average_rating\n           - JOIN reviews r ON b.business_id = r.business_id\n    ✅ message queue\n          - write incoming reviews to a message queue \n          - and then have a consumer update the average rating in a separate service\n          - add complexity\n    ✅ Period update with Cron job\n    ✅ ✅ Update the average rating as we receive new reviews\n         - add the new review to Review table \n         - and updating the average rating in Business table",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "How would you efficiently calculate and update the average rating for businesses\n    ❌ calculate the average rating on the fly\n           - AVG(r.rating) AS average_rating\n           - JOIN reviews r ON b.business_id = r.business_id\n    ✅ message queue\n          - write incoming reviews to a message queue \n          - and then have a consumer update the average rating in a separate service\n          - add complexity\n    ✅ Period update with Cron job\n    ✅ ✅ Update the average rating as we receive new reviews\n         - add the new review to Review table \n         - and updating the average rating in Business table",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "7EatwDX890f8iFt35A3AU",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 24695.5897887772,
      "y": 1446.6674476619514,
      "width": 881.8387451171875,
      "height": 125,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
